Valhi Inc, formed by the March 10 mergerof Amalgamated Sugar Co into LLC Corp, said it had unauditedpro-forma earnings of 72 mln dlrs, or 61 cts a share, for thesix months ended December 31.    Valhi said these results were prepared as if the merger hadoccurred July 1, 1986, and on substantially the same basis asthe pro-forma financial information in LLC's and Amalgamated'sjoint proxy statement dated February 10.    Valhi said it has about 117 mln common shares outstandingwith about 85 pct held by &lt;Contran Corp>. Reuter&#3;